---
title: Bacon & Basil Pesto Potato Salad with Parmesan & Almonds Quick Prep | Ready in 15 | Serves 2
description: We are stepping it up with this spin on the classic potato salad with crispy bacon, basil pesto and juicy tomatoes. Ready in 15 minutes, this salad is packed with flavour and can be prepped the day before or made on the spot for a quick lunch!
